{"html":"<br/>\n<h2>Fact Symbols with Injective Instances</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\">None</p><br/>\n<h2>Multiset Rewriting Rules</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) isend:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KU( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> K( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) irecv:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KD( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Setup:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~k ), Fr( ~id ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> OnlyOnce( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Reader( ~k, ~id ), !Tag( ~k, ~id ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) reader1:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~r1 ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Challenge( ~r1, &#39;Reader&#39; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( ~r1 ), Initiated( ~r1 ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) tag1:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( r1 ), Fr( ~r2 ), !Tag( ~k, ~id ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Response( ~k, &#39;Tag&#39; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( &lt;(~id⊕~r2), (~r2⊕h(&lt;r1, ~k&gt;))&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) reader2:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Initiated( ~r1 ), !Reader( ~k, ~id ), In( xoredhash ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Alive( ~k, &#39;Tag&#39; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Eq( xoredhash, (~id⊕h(&lt;~r1, ~k&gt;)) )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span></p><br/>\n<h2>Restrictions of the Set of Traces</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> equality:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>x y #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Eq( x, y ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>x <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> y<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// safety formula</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>x y #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Eq( x, y ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>x <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> y<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> unique:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>OnlyOnce( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">∧</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>OnlyOnce( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>#i <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// safety formula</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>OnlyOnce( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">∧</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>OnlyOnce( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>#i <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span></p><br/>\n","title":"Multiset rewriting rules and restrictions"}